                    </div>
                    <span>The book is well written and informative about the events of Powell's life and the geological survey in which Powell played such a major role. My primary disappointment with the book was that I felt I didn't know the person John W. Powell much better after reading the book. The book provided very little information about Powell's life outside of his work.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">An Enchanting Piece of Scholarship</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
